{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.1","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:1","prev_osis_id":"Lev.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-17: cf. (L\u00e9 9:18-21; 7:11-36.) H\u00e9 13:15. 1 Co 10:16-18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque quelqu\u2019un offrira \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel un sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces: S\u2019il offre du gros b\u00e9tail, m\u00e2le ou femelle, il l\u2019offrira sans d\u00e9faut, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.2.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.2","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:2","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate de la victime, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation; et les sacrificateurs, fils d\u2019Aaron, r\u00e9pandront le sang sur l\u2019autel tout autour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.3","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:3","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>De ce sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, il offrira en sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel: la graisse qui couvre les entrailles et toute celle qui y est attach\u00e9e;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.4","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:4","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>les deux rognons, et la graisse qui les entoure, qui couvre les flancs, et le grand lobe du foie, qu\u2019il d\u00e9tachera pr\u00e8s des rognons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.5","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:5","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les fils d\u2019Aaron br\u00fbleront cela sur l\u2019autel, par-dessus l\u2019holocauste qui sera sur le bois mis au feu. C\u2019est un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu, d\u2019une agr\u00e9able odeur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.6","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:6","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>S\u2019il offre du menu b\u00e9tail, m\u00e2le ou femelle, en sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, il l\u2019offrira sans d\u00e9faut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.7","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:7","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>S\u2019il offre en sacrifice un agneau, il le pr\u00e9sentera devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.8","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:8","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate de la victime, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera devant la tente d\u2019assignation; et les fils d\u2019Aaron en r\u00e9pandront le sang sur l\u2019autel tout autour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.9","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:9","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>De ce sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, il offrira en sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel: la graisse, la queue enti\u00e8re, qu\u2019il s\u00e9parera pr\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00e9chine, la graisse qui couvre les entrailles et toute celle qui y est attach\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.10","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:10","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>les deux rognons, et la graisse qui les entoure, qui couvre les flancs, et le grand lobe du foie, qu\u2019il d\u00e9tachera pr\u00e8s des rognons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.11","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:11","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le sacrificateur br\u00fblera cela sur l\u2019autel. C\u2019est l\u2019aliment d\u2019un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.12","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:12","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Si son offrande est une ch\u00e8vre, il la pr\u00e9sentera devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.13","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:13","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il posera sa main sur la t\u00eate de sa victime, qu\u2019il \u00e9gorgera devant la tente d\u2019assignation; et les fils d\u2019Aaron en r\u00e9pandront le sang sur l\u2019autel tout autour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.14","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:14","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>De la victime, il offrira en sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel: la graisse qui couvre les entrailles et toute celle qui y est attach\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.15","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:15","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>les deux rognons, et la graisse qui les entoure, qui couvre les flancs, et le grand lobe du foie, qu\u2019il d\u00e9tachera pr\u00e8s des rognons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.16","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:16","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le sacrificateur br\u00fblera cela sur l\u2019autel. Toute la graisse est l\u2019aliment d\u2019un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu, d\u2019une agr\u00e9able odeur \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.17","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 3:17","prev_osis_id":"Lev.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>C\u2019est ici une loi perp\u00e9tuelle pour vos descendants, dans tous les lieux o\u00f9 vous habiterez: vous ne mangerez ni graisse ni sang.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.4.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.3.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}